## Source: ossf-package-analysis (70dfdb1e0f7d12c7350dc620f464f42a4f856ae44b713e104c105ef2b481cae2)
The OpenSSF Package Analysis project identified 'airbnb-private' @ 10.0.1 (npm) as malicious.

It is considered malicious because:

- The package executes one or more commands associated with malicious behavior.
